'''Sultan Mandash''' ({{langx|ar|سلطان مندش}}; born October 17, 1994), is a Saudi Arabian [[association football|football]]er who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Al Hilal SFC|Al Hilal]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=سلطان مندش - Sultan Madash |url=https://extragoal.net/player/s-mandash}}</ref>

==Club career==
On 1 June 2024, Mandash joined [[Al-Taawoun FC|Al-Taawoun]] on a two-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=رسمياً.. التعاون يضم سلطان مندش |url=https://www.alyaum.com/article/6533172}}</ref>

On 11 January 2026, Mandash joined [[Al Hilal SFC|Al Hilal]] on a two-and-a-half year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title="سلطان مندش" هلاليًا لعامين ونصف |url=https://alhilal.com/ar/news/sltan-mndsh-hlalyana-laamyn-wnsf}}</ref>

